"the second quicktune."
msgstr "需要前一步骤的设置，应在第二次快速调谐前完成"

#: /home/runner/work/MethodicConfigurator/MethodicConfigurator/ardupilot_methodic_configurator/configuration_steps_strings.py:121
msgid ""
"Requires the setup step. It is easier to do before the FC is mounted in the "
