msgstr "需要设置步骤。在将飞控安装到飞行器之前进行更容易"

#: /home/runner/work/MethodicConfigurator/MethodicConfigurator/ardupilot_methodic_configurator/configuration_steps_strings.py:122
msgid ""
"Sometimes it depends on the remote controller. Configuring telemetry early "
